# Spartan UI

## Imports

From `@app/shared/ui/button`, `@app/shared/ui/dialog`, `@app/shared/ui/table`, etc.

Add new: `npx @spartan-ng/cli add <component>`

## Dialog state sync

```typescript
readonly dialogState = signal<'open' | 'closed'>('closed');

openCreate() {
  this.dialogState.set('closed');
  this.dialogState.set('open');
}

onDialogStateChanged(state: 'open' | 'closed') {
  this.dialogState.set(state);
}
```

Template: `<hlm-dialog [state]="dialogState()" (stateChanged)="onDialogStateChanged($event)">`

## CRUD layout

Header (title + primary button) → filter bar → `hlm-table` → create/edit dialog → delete dialog.

## Toasts

`toast.success('...')` / `toast.error('...')` from `ngx-sonner`.
